com.esri.mo2.data.feat
Interface SelectionSet

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, Searchable, Selectable
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseSelectionSet
public interface SelectionSet
extends Searchable, Selectable, Cloneable

A logical collection of Row objects obtained from a particular Table. Two SelectionSets can be combined to form a new SelectionSet based on various boolean operations, providing their Targets are identical.
